####文字小游戏功能介绍：
###目标为类，对象，方法的练习###
- 全局设置4个人物：①tangzhanglao（唐长老）②sunwukong（孙悟空）③zhubajie（猪八戒）④沙僧（shasheng）；
- 四个人物分别设置了不同的技能，汇总成EXP（战力）；
- 游戏功能分为：
    ①查看每个角色对于的EXP是多少；
    ②手动选择对手PK；
    ③自动选择对手PK；
    ④手动：一旦选择相同的对手会提示报错；
    ⑤自动：会自动筛选两个不同的角色来PK（排除掉一样的对手）；
    ⑥不管手动还是自动，一旦选择了tangzhanglao（唐长老）就可以叫一个帮手（helper），然后helper和另外一个对手再次PK；
    ⑦当抽取帮手时，只可以抽取除了tangzhanglao和PK2之外的帮手；
    ⑧输入错误会提示错误信息；

- 开始游戏：
```
pls choice the Number[1(CHECK EXP)/2(PK)/Quit For Exit]: 1
Pls input your Hero's Nick name: zhubajie
Zhubajie's EXP is 2130.0
pls choice the Number[1(CHECK EXP)/2(PK)/Quit For Exit]: 2
Two Mode: [1(PK by manual)/2(PK By Auto)]: 1
Pls input the PlayerA: zhubajie
Pls input the PlayerB: sunwukong
*********zhubajie PK sunwukong*********
Start PK ...
The Finally Result is ...
Congralations, sunwukong is a Winnwer
pls choice the Number[1(CHECK EXP)/2(PK)/Quit For Exit]: 2
Two Mode: [1(PK by manual)/2(PK By Auto)]: 1
Pls input the PlayerA: zhubajie
Pls input the PlayerB: tangzhanglao
*********zhubajie PK tangzhanglao*********
You can call a helper [Y/N]: y
Start PK ...
The Finally Result is ...
You're so luckcy the helper is sunwukong and You're a Winner!
pls choice the Number[1(CHECK EXP)/2(PK)/Quit For Exit]: 2
Two Mode: [1(PK by manual)/2(PK By Auto)]: 2
*********sunwukong PK zhubajie*********
Start PK ...
The Finally Result is ...
Congralations, sunwukong is a Winnwer
pls choice the Number[1(CHECK EXP)/2(PK)/Quit For Exit]: 2
Two Mode: [1(PK by manual)/2(PK By Auto)]: 2
*********shasheng PK tangzhanglao*********
You can call a helper [Y/N]: y
Start PK ...
The Finally Result is ...
Sorry, Unlucky the helper is shasheng You Lose it!!
pls choice the Number[1(CHECK EXP)/2(PK)/Quit For Exit]: 2
Two Mode: [1(PK by manual)/2(PK By Auto)]: 2
*********shasheng PK sunwukong*********
Start PK ...
The Finally Result is ...
Congralations, sunwukong is a Winnwer
pls choice the Number[1(CHECK EXP)/2(PK)/Quit For Exit]: 2
Two Mode: [1(PK by manual)/2(PK By Auto)]: 2
*********tangzhanglao PK sunwukong*********
You can call a helper [Y/N]: n
<Game Over>: 人生苦短，万事无常... 你被爱徒sunwukong干死了...
```


